easy-going-al-hayyin","tag-fear-al-khawf","tag-glad-tidings-al-bushra","tag-hardship","tag-manners-adab"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6Yv","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":17116,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/11\/dawah-glad-tidings-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":26815,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Da\u2019wah: Give glad tidings, make it easy, remain united","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Burdah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, sent him and Mu\u2019adh to Yemen, saying, \u201cMake things easy and do not make things difficult. Give glad tidings and do not repel people. Cooperate with each other and do not become divided.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2529,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/26\/prophet-good-akhlaq-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":26815,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: The Prophet teaches good character, manners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was never obscene or immoral. The Prophet would say, \"Verily, among the best of you are those with the best character.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3559, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2321 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":684,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/08\/prophet-never-said-uff\/","url_meta":{"origin":26815,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Manners: The Prophet never even said &#8216;Uff&#8217;","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: I served the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, for ten years. By Allah, he never even said to me, \u201cUff!\u201d He never said harshly, \u201cWhy did you do that?\u201d or, \u201cWhy did you not do that?\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2309 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/13\/when-a-hajji-dies-talbiya\/","url_meta":{"origin":26815,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: When someone dies while on the pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man performing the pilgrimage was thrown from his camel and died while we were with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u00a0The Prophet said, \u201cWash him with water mixed with the leaves of a lote tree and shroud him in his two garments. Do not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhaditho